In [103]:
months = [str(x) for x in df_use['campaign_month'].unique()]
years = [str(x) for x in df_use['campaign_year'].unique()]
fnames = list(itertools.product(years, months))
trends = functools.reduce(lambda x,y: x+y,[[x]*3 for x in range(1,13)])
trend_dict = dict(zip(fnames,trends))
df_use['campaign_trend'] = df_use['campaign_tuple'].apply(lambda x: trend_dict[x])
